title: Neighbours from Hell+Crack
description:
The first game from the "Neighbours from Hell" series by the JoWooD Productions. You play as the little, funny and very "creative" neghimbor,Woody, of the big, strong and dumb Rottweiler. You got furious at him and decided to assault him with pranks, and you invited a TV shooting team to shoot what you are doing... so if you do well you'll become a TV star!

1.Download the file
2.Burn or mount 
3.Install the game
4.Go to "Crack" file
5.Copy the game file
6.Replace the original
7.Enjoy the game
8.Seed it
